The '''Ka'aa''' were a sapient species, known for wandering the stars. And were thought old enough to have seen the youngest stars of the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]] come into being. The called the Koornacht cluster, ''No'aat padu'll'', which translated to the Little Nursery.<ref name="BtS">''[[Before the Storm]]''</ref>

